Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Network simulator services won't start

Solution: Check if ports are already in use with netstat -tulpn. Use different ports if needed.
Issue: PowerShell scripts fail with permission errors

Solution: Ensure scripts are executable: chmod +x script.ps1. Run with pwsh -File script.ps1.
Issue: BloodHound data analysis produces empty results

Solution: Verify JSON files are properly formatted. Check that relationships reference valid node IDs.
Issue: Graph visualization fails

Solution: Install matplotlib if missing: pip3 install matplotlib networkx. Ensure output directory exists.
Issue: Pivot scanner returns no candidates

Solution: Verify network data includes connectivity information. Check scoring thresholds aren't too restrictive.
